reviews.review_text: I can't believe... ...I'm the first to review this version. It sounds great - probably one of the best I've heard from '70-'72.

ugh One of these day the freds will learn.  This is a COMPOSITE.  That means BOTH Soundboard & Audience recording make up this show.  Its a subpar AUD recording at best.  Did either of you listen to Stella Blue??  Evidently not.
